{"id":188708,"type":2,"name":"トッポジージョ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/78/b5/188708_57Od0.jpg","summary":"1988年版テレビアニメ版の第1作。\r\n当初は朝日放送と日本アニメーションの共同製作で、1988年4月27日から同年9月21日までテレビ朝日系列局で放送されていたが（水曜 18:50 - 19:20）、1988年10月7日放送分からはテレビ東京と日本アニメーションの共同製作になり、タイトルも『夢見るトッポ・ジージョ』に変更。以後は同年12月30日までテレビ東京系列局で放送されていた（金曜 18:30 - 19:00）。キャストとスタッフは基本的に朝日放送製作時代と同じだった。\r\n本作でのトッポ・ジージョは未来の宇宙飛行士で、現代のイタリアへタイムスリップしたという設定。トッポ・ジージョのキャラクター以外、ストーリーは完全なアニメオリジナルである。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>飞飞鼠</li><li><span>话数: </span>21</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1988-4-27</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>21</li><li><span>美术设计: </span><a href=\"/person/30356\">川本征平</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Topo Gigio</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1988-9-21</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"1988","count":2},{"name":"1988年四月番","count":1},{"name":"1988年","count":1},{"name":"1988年4月","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":652634,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652634","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652635,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652635","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652636,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652636","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652637,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652637","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652638,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652638","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652639,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652639","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652640,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652640","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652641,"url":"http://bgm.